stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> Verifying: 提交验证
    Verifying --> Ready: 全部门禁通过
    Verifying --> Rejected: 任一硬门禁失败

    Ready --> Canary: 启动灰度
    Canary --> Partial: 扩大流量
    Canary --> RolledBack: 指标异常

    Partial --> Full: 全量发布
    Partial --> RolledBack: 指标异常

    Full --> RolledBack: 生产异常
    RolledBack --> Archived
    Rejected --> Draft: 修复后重新提交
